  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find risk factors for hemorrhagic stroke, specifically
      intracerebral hemorrhage (ICH), among Caucasians, African Americans, and Hispanics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
